00:38:54,830 --> 00:38:55,310
I will get in first.

851
00:38:55,310 --> 00:38:56,200
You get in first.

852
00:38:56,600 --> 00:38:56,910
Alright.

853
00:39:12,760 --> 00:39:13,720
Guan Chao, you're doing not bad.

854
00:39:13,720 --> 00:39:15,280
What a nice little car.

855
00:39:15,600 --> 00:39:16,510
Nothing special about it.

856
00:39:19,760 --> 00:39:20,350
But,

857
00:39:20,350 --> 00:39:21,430
I'm sorry.

858
00:39:22,120 --> 00:39:24,120
Mingyu and Jiang Yi are quite busy.

859
00:39:24,120 --> 00:39:25,560
They still couldn't make it.

860
00:39:27,430 --> 00:39:28,240
That's all right.

861
00:39:28,240 --> 00:39:29,240
I'm very happy for

862
00:39:29,240 --> 00:39:30,280
having you two here.

863
00:39:31,350 --> 00:39:32,120
Zhuang Yuan,

864
00:39:32,120 --> 00:39:33,160
why are you quiet?

865
00:39:33,680 --> 00:39:34,200
You'll be my best man.

866
00:39:34,600 --> 00:39:35,470
That's a must.

867
00:39:36,950 --> 00:39:37,830
Yingzi,

868
00:39:38,350 --> 00:39:39,720
you might as well be the bridesmaid.

869
00:39:42,310 --> 00:39:42,990
About that...

870
00:39:43,160 --> 00:39:44,120
Yang Fan's cousin

871
00:39:44,470 --> 00:39:44,910
wants to be the bridesmaid too.

872
00:39:44,910 --> 00:39:45,560
No problem.

873
00:39:45,910 --> 00:39:47,600
We can get more than one bridesmaid.

874
00:39:49,200 --> 00:39:49,990
I...

875
00:39:50,160 --> 00:39:52,120
Stop talking nonsense
when you know nothing.

876
00:39:52,830 --> 00:39:53,430
I'm sorry.

877
00:39:53,430 --> 00:39:56,080
Bridesmaids must be either friends
or family of the bride.

878
00:39:56,080 --> 00:39:58,240
How can I be the bridesmaid
when I'm friends with the groom?

879
00:39:58,560 --> 00:39:59,240
Don't listen to him.

880
00:40:01,160 --> 00:40:01,510
Guys,

881
00:40:01,510 --> 00:40:02,600
I'll take you home
to put your luggage first.

882
00:40:02,990 --> 00:40:03,910
When you're done packing

883
00:40:04,200 --> 00:40:04,800
and my class is over,

884
00:40:05,030 --> 00:40:05,990
let's go to get some dumplings
at Grandma's place.

885
00:40:06,280 --> 00:40:06,470
Sure.

886
00:40:06,470 --> 00:40:07,030
Okay.

887
00:40:22,240 --> 00:40:23,080
Mom!

888
00:40:23,350 --> 00:40:24,510
Coming!

889
00:40:24,950 --> 00:40:25,680
Open the door!

890
00:40:26,080 --> 00:40:27,030
Here I come.

891
00:40:28,430 --> 00:40:29,240
My daughter,

892
00:40:29,240 --> 00:40:30,910
I've missed you so much.

893
00:40:31,510 --> 00:40:32,240
Huang Qifa!

894
00:40:32,240 --> 00:40:33,240
Your daughter is back!

895
00:40:33,240 --> 00:40:34,640
I'm cooking.

896
00:40:34,640 --> 00:40:36,870
I can't believe my dad is cooking!

897
00:40:37,240 --> 00:40:38,680
Your mother said I know nothing

898
00:40:38,680 --> 00:40:40,200
and made me choose
between cooking

899
00:40:40,200 --> 00:40:41,120
and square dancing.

900
00:40:41,120 --> 00:40:42,990
You made the smart choice to cook.

901
00:40:42,990 --> 00:40:44,350
I chose square dancing.

902
00:40:48,680 --> 00:40:49,720
Daughter,

903
00:40:49,720 --> 00:40:51,240
come have some water.

904
00:40:51,720 --> 00:40:52,350
Sit here.

905
00:40:52,350 --> 00:40:53,200
I want to ask you something.

906
00:40:53,200 --> 00:40:53,720
Here.

907
00:40:53,990 --> 00:40:55,030
What is it?

908
00:40:55,470 --> 00:40:56,910
I heard that Jiang Yi
has returned to China.

909
00:40:56,910 --> 00:40:57,800
He is now in Jiangzhou.

910
00:40:58,910 --> 00:40:59,990
How do you know that?

911
00:41:00,280 --> 00:41:00,990
Who told you that?

912
00:41:01,560 --> 00:41:03,200
Anything going on in Hangtian City

913
00:41:03,200 --> 00:41:04,600
can't pass through your mom's ears.

914
00:41:06,470 --> 00:41:06,950
Jiang Yi

915
00:41:06,950 --> 00:41:09,030
is not staying in Hangtian City anymore.

916
00:41:09,200 --> 00:41:11,430
Is he coming back
for Guan Chao's wedding?

917
00:41:13,510 --> 00:41:14,200
He is busy with work.

918
00:41:14,200 --> 00:41:14,990
He is not coming back.

919
00:41:15,640 --> 00:41:17,830
Speaking of Jiang Yi, I think

920
00:41:17,830 --> 00:41:19,680
he makes a good match for our daughter.

921
00:41:22,310 --> 00:41:22,510
Dad.

922
00:41:22,510 --> 00:41:23,800
Don't talk nonsense.

923
00:41:23,800 --> 00:41:24,990
I'm suing you for defamation.

924
00:41:25,720 --> 00:41:27,200
Jiang Yi has been abroad
for so many years,

925
00:41:27,200 --> 00:41:28,390
is he still single?

926
00:41:28,990 --> 00:41:30,390
I don't know.

927
00:41:30,390 --> 00:41:31,310
I didn't ask him.

928
00:41:31,310 --> 00:41:32,910
You added Jiang Yi on WeChat, no?

929
00:41:33,680 --> 00:41:34,390
Yeah.

930
00:41:34,390 --> 00:41:35,350
What do you want with it?

931
00:41:35,830 --> 00:41:37,470
Well, let me talk to him.

932
00:41:37,760 --> 00:41:38,390
No way.

933
00:41:38,950 --> 00:41:40,390
Just one sentence.

934
00:41:40,390 --> 00:41:41,430
Give me.

935
00:41:46,080 --> 00:41:46,830
Don't say nonsense.

936
00:41:50,640 --> 00:41:50,990
Hello,

937
00:41:51,800 --> 00:41:52,720
Jiang Yi.

938
00:41:52,910 --> 00:41:53,990
It's me, Madam Guo.

939
00:41:55,160 --> 00:41:56,680
I heard you are back.

940
00:41:56,680 --> 00:41:57,990
When are you free?

941
00:41:57,990 --> 00:41:58,950
Do pay me a visit when you're free.

942
00:41:58,950 --> 00:41:59,950
I quite miss you.

943
00:41:59,950 --> 00:42:01,200
I will make you
something delicious to eat.

944
00:42:01,600 --> 00:42:02,800
That's enough.

945
00:42:03,350 --> 00:42:05,120
I'm sure he's back in England by now.

946
00:42:06,870 --> 00:42:07,510
Has he replied yet?

947
00:42:09,990 --> 00:42:10,800
(Sure, madam.)

948
00:42:14,390 --> 00:42:15,030
Let me have a look.

949
00:42:15,030 --> 00:42:15,560
Let me.

950
00:42:16,080 --> 00:42:16,720
Look.

951
00:42:16,720 --> 00:42:17,390
He said yes.

952
00:42:18,280 --> 00:42:19,720
He was being polite.

953
00:42:20,430 --> 00:42:21,470
Do you understand?

954
00:42:21,800 --> 00:42:22,640
I'm a little tired.

955
00:42:22,640 --> 00:42:23,910
I'm going to lie down for a while.

956
00:42:23,910 --> 00:42:25,080
Call me when dinner's ready.

957
00:42:25,080 --> 00:42:26,030
Can't you lie later?

958
00:42:26,030 --> 00:42:27,280
The dinner's almost ready.
